        "content": "<p>This is expected. <code>open Foo</code> opens the namespace <code>Foo</code> and activates scoped attributes in <code>Foo</code>.<br>\n<code>open scoped Foo</code> just activates the scoped attributes. Example:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">namespace</span> <span class=\"n\">Foo</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">foo</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">id</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"mi\">10</span>\n<span class=\"n\">scoped</span> <span class=\"kd\">prefix</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">20</span> <span class=\"s2\">\" `` \"</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">foo</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span> <span class=\"n\">Foo</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span> <span class=\"n\">scoped</span> <span class=\"n\">Foo</span>\n<span class=\"k\">#check</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- Error</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span> <span class=\"n\">Foo</span>\n<span class=\"k\">#check</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- Ok</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
